          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "The most impactful timing decision for men over 40 is breakfast. Getting 30 grams of protein at the first meal of the day — after an overnight fast when muscle protein synthesis is low — provides the strongest daily return. After that, spreading protein evenly across meals matters more than any specific timing window."
